{"tid":1438412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[代po]  癡撚線 未來一個月日日都會有遊行","createTime":"2019-08-09T18:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T18:24:01.000Z","uid":277955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"54bdcafece46695d945e63b0a80b719b9b6b9703","tid":1438412,"uid":277955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:14:17.000Z","msg":"作為一個奉公守法 愛国愛党嘅連登仔<br />\n為咗避免違犯公安條例唔知第幾多條嘅非法集結<br />\n我係度呼籲大家進行任何集會遊行之前都申請咗不反對通知書先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 Bbq 行街 或者返大陸飲喜茶等等<br />\n你知啦 Bbq有火㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一陣無不反對 俾人以為我哋係暴徒 放火 <br />\n容乜易俾人起訴非法集結或者暴動㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我平時行街又鍾意約埋成班波牛一齊 <br />\n一陣間行路霸多咗位 <br />\n俾人屌我哋進行未經批准嘅遊行就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23856d89dcf4dcb493cfd95c458b7132b6bbe2c0","tid":1438412,"uid":277955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:14:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"48746919404758a6d200a10859d349f7d32867e9","tid":1438412,"uid":277955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:14:54.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"8e6d4fc72cddd00f9c4be75f27fd45916de152cd","tid":1438412,"uid":277955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b518cd0a7665655db14b83652ea628697190bf07","tid":1438412,"uid":277955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:15:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"6b5cdebd88b901fd308bdd8253c85bf931e26265","tid":1438412,"uid":277955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:15:32.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"7190135663ce081902f775c8068d16707ed8c5cc","tid":1438412,"uid":277955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:16:45.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"ed8398bffe98ff0b9b14282616e35feede06402e","tid":1438412,"uid":277955,"like":0,"dislike